data.description: Discover the epitome of comfortable living in this 3 bed/2 bath, 1554 sq ft ranch-style pool home that invites you to explore endless possibilities! Immerse yourself in a realm of potential as you navigate the recently renovated open-plan eat-in kitchen, featuring modern stainless steel appliances and a pantry with convenient rolling shelves. The residence is equipped with Hurricane-resistant windows, an investment of approximately $16k. Embrace the distinctive charm of the split floor plan, providing a haven in the private primary bedroom and en-suite. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized, and the guest bathroom boasts a tub/shower combo. This jewel is primed for your personal touch, with ample space for additional upgrades to turn it into your dream retreat. Offered "As Is," this home serves as the perfect canvas for expressing your creativity. Immerse yourself in the heated pool, soak up the sun in the backyard, and enjoy the community's appeal, complemented by low quarterly HOA fees. Seize the opportunity to customize this residence and embark on a journey of limitless living!
